{
  "texts": [
    "It is also possible to give the AI model specific character roles to obtain responses in a certain style or level of detail.",
    "For example, you could instruct the model to behave like a classical composer or a modern artist.",
    "Alternatively, you could ask it to take on the role of an experienced engineer or a passionate biologist.",
    "These types of impersonation make it possible to generate responses that are adapted not only in content but also in expression and perspective to the chosen role, which can lead to a more diverse and creative exchange.",
    "To limit the scope of valid answers, good examples from another domain can be provided in the context in order to transfer the style or type of answer to the actual query."
  ]
}